MBOMBELA &#8211; He walked into the door and the little girl asked him, &#8220;Are you Jesus? My mother told me Jesus would fetch my grandfather.&#8221; This is just one account Andrie Homann, owner of Martins Funeral Services, has encountered while doing his job.Homann is a large man who displays a solid stability with a quiet demeanour, and is visibly someone people feel they can lean on in the worst of times.